title: Kim Fowley - Outrageous (1968) + Good Clean Fun (1969) (1995) [F
description:
underground....psychedleic....pre-punk...glam-rock

"My names is Kim Fowley.
I've been given up for dead,
my rock 'n' roll can save your soul,
by painting pictures in your empty head."
